8813a2390d58c1c7.poster.avif?t=1670014796\" width=620 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232420/extras/7b7c32f295b40d758813a2390d58c1c7.webm?t=1670014796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2232420/extras/7b7c32f295b40d758813a2390d58c1c7.mp4?t=1670014796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Depending on your gameplay, the game can have multiple endings! Your actions will change how the environment acts — against or for you!",
